      "span_text": "Hyperimmune plasma was obtained from a convalescent common marmoset (Callithrix jacchus) from a previous experiment [CITATION_1] ) inoculated with 5.2 Â 10 6 TCID 50 MERS-CoV via the intratracheal, intranasal, ocular and oral route, then inoculated with 5.2 Â 10 6 TCID 50 MERS-CoV on 20 dpi via the intratracheal route and finally inoculated with 5.2 Â 10 6 TCID 50 MERSCoV adjuvated with Titermax Gold (Sigma Aldrich) on 41 dpi via the intramuscular route.",
